translate french danaq4_93bacd33:

    # cw "Do you think Mrs. Mills knows about us?"
    cw "Tu crois que Mme Mills est au courant pour nous ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:15
translate french danaq4_6b67efaa:

    # pc "She hasn't said anything to me about it. Do you think she would care?"
    pc "Elle ne m'en a pas parlé. Tu crois que ça l'intéresserait ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:17
translate french danaq4_26c97420:

    # cw "Probably! She's so strict."
    cw "Probablement ! Elle est tellement stricte."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:18
translate french danaq4_e21be69c:

    # cw "She'd probably fire us both."
    cw "Elle nous virerait sûrement tous les deux."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:20
translate french danaq4_b14300d9:

    # cw "And I can't get fired. I have rent to pay now."
    cw "Et je ne peux pas me faire virer. J'ai un loyer à payer maintenant."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:23
translate french danaq4_22d4233b:

    # pc "Mrs. Mills really isn't that bad, you know?"
    pc "Mme Mills n'est pas si terrible que ça, tu sais ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:25
translate french danaq4_105e9399:

    # pc "I think she'd be a little more understanding. I don't think she'd fire us."
    pc "Je pense qu'elle serait un peu plus compréhensive. Je ne crois pas qu'elle nous virerait."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:26
translate french danaq4_f8826d17:

    # cw "If you say so. She's always seemed pretty mean to me."
    cw "Si tu le dis. Elle m'a toujours semblé assez méchante."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:27
translate french danaq4_b63ff6eb:

    # pc "Oh yeah. She's mean, but she can be nice too."
    pc "Oh oui. Elle est méchante, mais elle peut aussi être gentille."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:28
translate french danaq4_845ad89c:

    # pc "She's not all bad."
    pc "Elle n'est pas si mauvaise que ça."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:30
translate french danaq4_3c749a81:

    # cw "Well, I'd rather she just not find out at all."
    cw "Eh bien, je préférerais qu'elle ne le découvre pas du tout."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:31
translate french danaq4_8a1de4cc:

    # pc "Yeah, that works for me too."
    pc "Ouais, ça me va aussi."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:34
translate french danaq4_6f0480be:

    # cw "Yeah, good plan."
    cw "Ouais, c'est un bon plan."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:36
translate french danaq4_52d7409a:

    # cw "We need to be more careful at work."
    cw "On doit faire plus attention au travail."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:37
translate french danaq4_9fe5788c:

    # cw "We've been too reckless. It's been fun, but we have to be more careful."
    cw "On a été trop imprudents. C'était sympa, mais on doit faire plus attention."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:38
translate french danaq4_390b4a1e:

    # pc "So no more sex at work?"
    pc "Alors, plus de sexe au travail ?"

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:40
translate french danaq4_c66d4448:

    # cw "Now let's not go crazy here."
    cw "N'exagérons pas."

# game/Scenes/Dana/DanaConversation/danaq4.rpy:41
translate french danaq4_1a9c1fe0:

    # cw "Just more careful."
    cw "Juste plus de prudence."

